511
00:26:18,535 --> 00:26:19,802
Toby, it happened to me.

512
00:26:19,837 --> 00:26:22,060
It didn't happen to you.

513
00:26:30,333 --> 00:26:31,466
(KATE SIGHS)

514
00:26:31,599 --> 00:26:35,185
