and thinking, "Wow.

516
00:26:40,524 --> 00:26:42,044
She's having our baby."

517
00:26:44,619 --> 00:26:46,747
And then I blinked, and I remembered.

518
00:26:48,498 --> 00:26:50,499
And I slid out of bed
as quietly as possible

519
00:26:50,534 --> 00:26:52,802
