00:28:10,138 --> 00:28:11,279
Mom.

545
00:28:11,824 --> 00:28:13,943
I'm sorry I didn't
tell you about Berklee.

546
00:28:14,758 --> 00:28:15,974
It's just...

547
00:28:17,677 --> 00:28:19,177
you know, if I don't get in...

548
00:28:20,146 --> 00:28:21,552
