558
00:28:59,405 --> 00:29:01,287
She was just a...

559
00:29:02,122 --> 00:29:03,763
closed steel door.

560
00:29:04,865 --> 00:29:06,268
And even if you could get through,

561
00:29:06,303 --> 00:29:09,419
